OL,3,CTrump reviewing Iran's peace proposal
OL,4,Cbut doubts 'it would be acceptable'
OL,6,FPresident Donald Trump has said he is
OL,7,Freviewing a new peace proposal from
OL,8,FIran, but expressed skepticism that it
OL,9,Fcould lead to a deal between the two
OL,10,Fnations.
OL,12,FIran has sent a 14-point proposal to
OL,13,Fthe US via Pakistan, in response to a
OL,14,Fnine-point American proposal,
OL,15,Faccording to reports from two semi-
OL,16,Fofficial Iranian news outlets linked
OL,17,Fto the Revolutionary Guard.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1777791916
OL,3,CTrump reviewing Iran's peace proposal
OL,4,Cbut doubts 'it would be acceptable'
OL,6,FTrump rejected a previous Iranian
OL,7,Fproposal this week, and wrote on
OL,8,Fsocial media that he doubted the
OL,9,Fnewest version "would be acceptable"
OL,10,Fon Saturday evening.
OL,12,F"I will soon be reviewing the plan
OL,13,Fthat Iran has just sent to us, but
OL,14,Fcan't imagine that it would be
OL,15,Facceptable in that they have not yet
OL,16,Fpaid a big enough price for what they
OL,17,Fhave done to Humanity, and the World,
OL,18,Fover the last 47 years," the post on
OL,19,FTruth Social read.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
