OL,3,CTrump reviewing Iran's peace proposal
OL,4,Cbut doubts 'it would be acceptable'
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FThe US and Iran struck a ceasefire
OL,12,Fagreement on April 7, and the nations
OL,13,Fhave not traded fire since then.
OL,15,FHowever, the US has been engaged in a
OL,16,Fnaval blockade of Iranian ports along
OL,17,Fthe Strait of Hormuz since April 13,
OL,18,Fin response to Iran almost entirely
OL,19,Fclosing the waterway to the rest of
OL,20,Fthe world.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
