OL,3,CTrump reviewing Iran's peace proposal
OL,4,Cbut doubts 'it would be acceptable'
OL,6,FTrump also announced on Saturday that
OL,7,Fthe US will reduce its military
OL,8,Fpresence in Germany even further,
OL,9,Fafter the Pentagon confirmed 5,000
OL,10,Ftroops would withdraw from the country
OL,11,Fover the next year.
OL,13,FThe president didn't offer an
OL,14,Fexplanation, but said an even bigger
OL,15,Freduction was coming, as he seeks to
OL,16,Fscale back America's commitment to
OL,17,FEuropean security.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
