OL,3,CTrump reviewing Iran's peace proposal
OL,4,Cbut doubts 'it would be acceptable'
OL,6,FMeanwhile Israel and Lebanon's
OL,7,Fmilitant Hezbollah group have kept up
OL,8,Ftheir attacks despite having a
OL,9,Fceasefire in place since April 17.
OL,11,FIsrael's military on Saturday issued a
OL,12,Fnew warning for residents of nine
OL,13,Fsouthern villages to evacuate.
OL,15,FMore troops removed from Germany
OL,17,FTrump has said the US will reduce its
OL,18,Ftroop presence in Germany even further
OL,19,Fthan the 5,000 the Pentagon announced
OL,20,Fwould be withdrawing on Friday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
