PN,30206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1777791916
OL,3,CTrump reviewing Iran's peace proposal
OL,4,Cbut doubts 'it would be acceptable'
OL,6,F"We're going to cut way down. And
OL,7,Fwe're cutting a lot further than
OL,8,F5,000," Trump told reporters in
OL,9,FFlorida on Saturday.
OL,11,FBoris Pistorius, Germany's defense
OL,12,Fminister, had appeared to take the
OL,13,Finitial news about troops withdrawing
OL,14,Fin his stride, stating that the
OL,15,Fdrawback was expected.
OL,17,F"The presence of American soldiers in
OL,18,FEurope, and especially in Germany, is
OL,19,Fin our interest and in the interest of
OL,20,Fthe US," Pistorius told the German
OL,21,Fnews agency dpa.
OL,26,@nD@AOUyD@AOU|D@HO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/11
