OL,3,CTrump reviewing Iran's peace proposal
OL,4,Cbut doubts 'it would be acceptable'
OL,6,F"If we are to remain transatlantic, we
OL,7,Fmust strengthen the European pillar
OL,8,Fwithin Nato," he said.
OL,10,FThe US has a significant military
OL,11,Fpresence in Germany, with more than
OL,12,F36,000 active duty troops assigned to
OL,13,Fbases across the country as of last
OL,14,FDecember.
OL,16,FDepending on operations, exercises and
OL,17,Ftroop rotations, around 80,000-100,000
OL,18,FUS personnel are usually stationed in
OL,19,FEurope.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/11
