OL,6,FUS sends arms to Israel, Qatar, UAE
OL,7,Fand Kuwait
OL,9,FThe Trump administration has fast-
OL,10,Ftracked billions of dollars in arms
OL,11,Fsales to its Middle East allies, the
OL,12,FUS State Department has said in a
OL,13,Fseries of statements.
OL,15,FThe total cost of the weapons comes to
OL,16,Fmore than $8 billion (about #5.8
OL,17,Fbillion), with Secretary of State
OL,18,FMarco Rubio invoking emergency powers
OL,19,Fto approve the sales.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
