SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1777791916
OL,3,CTrump reviewing Iran's peace proposal
OL,4,Cbut doubts 'it would be acceptable'
OL,6,FAmong the items are Advanced Precision
OL,7,FKill Weapon Systems (APKWS) - made up
OL,8,Fof rocket launchers with laser-
OL,9,Fprecision and high explosive war heads
OL,10,F- given to the United Arab Emirates
OL,11,F(UAE) for an estimated $147.6 million
OL,12,F(about #108 million), to Israel for
OL,13,F$992.4 million (#729.5 million) and to
OL,14,FQatar for $992.4 million.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
