OL,3,CTrump reviewing Iran's peace proposal
OL,4,Cbut doubts 'it would be acceptable'
OL,6,FQatar will also receive Patriot
OL,7,Fmissiles $4.01 billion (#2.95 billion)
OL,8,Fand Kuwait will receive an Integrated
OL,9,FBattle Command System - which can
OL,10,Fdetect, track, and intercept air and
OL,11,Fmissile threats -for $2.5 billion
OL,12,F(#1.84 billion).
OL,14,FThe US will also supply non-major
OL,15,Fdefense equipment items such as
OL,16,Ftechnical data, spare and repair
OL,17,Fparts, personnel training, logistics
OL,18,Fsupport and transportation, the state
OL,19,Fdepartment said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/11
